LUXURIOUS
ELEGANT
DEPENDABLE
Here's air travel as you dreamed it
could be—and it's yours to enjoy
now! TWA's great new Jetstream
fleet offers superlative luxury,
superb service on swift non-stop
flights across the Atlantic between
New York and London, Paris,
Lisbon and Rome, coast-to-coast
in the U.S., and via the Polar Route
between Europe and California.
On your very next trip, be sure to
fly the finest…fly TWA Jetstream!
SEE YOUR TRAVEL AGENT

ervations via TWA Jetstream ...
arrange for hotel accommodations
everywhere you go, give you any
travel information you require.
